@base = http://127.0.0.1:8000

###
# ✅ Caso OK (200): item_id existe
GET {{base}}/items/foo
Accept: application/json

###
# ❌ Caso error (404): item_id NO existe → HTTPException
GET {{base}}/items/bar
Accept: application/json

###
# ❌ Otro inexistente (404)
GET {{base}}/items/xyz
Accept: application/json
